summary: This document is an email chain between Assistant United States Attorneys in the Southern District of New York discussing draft notes for an upcoming conference, likely related to the Epstein case. It references a victim interview and includes questions or issues that may arise.

events.title: Conference preparation

keyFacts: The document is an email chain dated August 26, 2019, between Assistant United States Attorneys in the Southern District of New York.
It discusses draft notes for a conference scheduled for August 27, 2019, and references a victim interview.
The email includes comments and questions that may arise during the conference, indicating ongoing legal proceedings related to the Epstein case.
